# Git
.git
.gitignore

# Runtime SQLite database (can be multi-GB) — never needed for the build
**/scanner.db
**/scanner.db-wal
**/scanner.db-shm
**/*.db
**/*.db-wal
**/*.db-shm

# Build outputs / release artifacts (produced BY the build, not inputs)
dist/
out/
synscan/synscan
grabber/grab
grabber/grab.exe
datastore/datastore
datastore/datastore.exe

# Docs and local tooling (not needed to compile)
docs/
*.md
.claude/

# NOTE: datastore/geoip/*.mmdb is intentionally NOT ignored —
# it is embedded into the datastore binary via //go:embed (see datastore/embed.go).
